title: Franck Chevallier
text: Franck Chevallier (born 3 January 1964) is a French <a href="hurdling">hurdler</a>. He competed in the <a href="Athletics%20at%20the%201984%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20110%20metres%20hurdles">men's 110 metres hurdles</a> at the <a href="1984%20Summer%20Olympics">1984 Summer Olympics</a>.
